## 4. HERO FLOW NARRATIVE (for proposal writer)

The three-frame story:

Frame 1 (01-02): "See the problem solved"
  User sees XML file uploaded, format instantly detected, memory chart animates to show
  streaming parser holding at 12 MB while naive approach would climb to 10GB+. The visual
  proof of scalability is immediate and concrete.

Frame 2 (03-04): "Reconciliation detail at your fingertips"
  Rules engine shows 170-rule evaluation at a glance. Red badges highlight failures (R03,
  R04, R07, R09). Click any rule to drill into the exact transactions and deltas. No hunting
  through logs. No black-box output. Every decision is traceable.

Frame 3 (05-06): "Analytics and export ready"
  Dashboard summarizes the health of the compliance state. Trend chart shows anomalies over
  time. Full ledger is pageable, sortable, and exportable. This is the state that finance
  teams live in day-to-day.

